#: givefood/templates/public/page.html:78
msgid "About us"
msgstr ""

#: givefood/templates/public/about_us.html:25
msgid ""
"\n"
"                <p>Give Food is a UK charity that uses data to highlight "
"local and structural food insecurity, then provides tools to help alleviate "
"it.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>We run the only <a href=\"/needs/\">national public "
"database of food banks</a>, tracking in realtime what they are requesting to "
"have donated.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Working with a wide variety of public and private "
"organisations, including many other charities, we share our data with "
"millions of users each year, helping people learn about and engage with food "
"poverty causes.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>We became a <a href=\"https://register-of-charities."
"charitycommission.gov.uk/en/charity-search/-/charity-"
"details/5147019\">charity</a> in February 2020, just weeks before the UK "
"entered COVID-19 lockdowns, and since then we've worked with hundreds of "
"local food insecurity alleviation organisations delivering hundreds of "
"tonnes of vitally needed supplies.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>For example, during the pandemic we delivered <a "
"href=\"/2020/#ppe-supplies\">1.2m items of PPE</a> to help keep food banks "
"from Penzance to Lerwick as safe as possible whilst continuing to support "
"their communities.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>We help the public act on food insecurity by using our "
"data to show which food banks are in their parliamentary constituency, and "
"provide a <a href=\"/write/\">tool to easily email their Member of "
"Parliament</a> asking what action they are taking to remedy it.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Our operations are open source and transparent, with "
"almost all of our current and historical <a href=\"https://github.com/"
"givefood/givefood\">code</a> and <a href=\"/api/\">data</a> published, plus "
"<a href=\"https://register-of-charities.charitycommission.gov.uk/charity-"
"search/-/charity-details/5147019/accounts-and-annual-returns\">accounts</a> "
"and <a href=\"/annual-reports/\">annual reports</a> available to view.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Please don't hesitate to contact us with any suggestions, "
"comments, criticism or encouragement.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    <em>The Give Food Trustees</em>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    <a href=\"mailto:mail@givefood.org.uk\">mail@givefood."
"org.uk</a>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"\n"
"            "
msgstr ""

